OL,6,FThe chairman of Southport mosque
OL,7,Fbelieves anyone who abuses social
OL,8,Fmedia by spreading misinformation
OL,9,Fshould be prosecuted.
OL,11,FAn Imam whose mosque was targeted by
OL,12,Frioters following the Southport
OL,13,Fattacks has said people who spread
OL,14,Fmisinformation on social media "should
OL,15,Fface the full force of the law".
