OL,6,FThe chairman of Southport mosque
OL,7,FIbrahim Hussein was trapped inside the
OL,8,Fbuilding with several others as
OL,9,Frioters hurled missiles and shouted
OL,10,F"vile" abuse at the place of worship
OL,11,Fin July 2024.
OL,13,FThe disorder unfolded after the murder
OL,14,Fof three little girls, six-year-old
OL,15,FBebe King, Elsie Dot Stancombe, seven,
OL,16,Fand nine-year-old Alice da Silva
OL,17,FAguiar.
