OL,6,FA report from the Home Affairs
OL,7,FCommittee has highlighted how an
OL,8,Finformation vacuum online "allowed
OL,9,Fdisinformation to flourish" about the
OL,10,Fthen unnamed suspect's nationality and
OL,11,Freligion.
OL,13,F"These people are always looking for
OL,14,Fan excuse so as soon as they find a
OL,15,Fvacuum they fill it with their own
OL,16,Flies, deceptions and hatred," Imam
OL,17,FHussein said.
