OL,6,F"Any review into the havoc that
OL,7,Fhappened last summer is absolutely
OL,8,Fwelcome. Social media should be
OL,9,Freigned in and if they're giving power
OL,10,Fto the police to do so, that can only
OL,11,Fbe welcomed by us."
OL,13,FThe report said the Crown Prosecution
OL,14,FService (CPS) and Merseyside Police
OL,15,Fwere ultimately limited on what they
OL,16,Fcould publish about killer, Axel
OL,17,FRudakubana, by the Contempt of Court
OL,18,FAct, which prevents the publication of
OL,19,Finformation that could prejudice
OL,20,Fcriminal proceedings.
