OL,6,FThe Commons committee welcomed a
OL,7,Freview into the law by the Law
OL,8,FCommission, which published a
OL,9,Fconsultation paper in March to
OL,10,Fconsider "whether there should be
OL,11,Fcontempt of court liability for those
OL,12,Fwho risk prejudicing a criminal trial
OL,13,Fby releasing information in the
OL,14,Finterests of public safety or national
OL,15,Fsecurity".
