OL,6,FMerseyside Police Chief Constable
OL,7,FSerena Kennedy told the committee that
OL,8,Fshe wanted to dispel misinformation in
OL,9,Fthe immediate aftermath of the murders
OL,10,Fby releasing information about
OL,11,FRudakubana's but was told not to by
OL,12,Flocal crown prosecutors.
OL,14,F"From my understanding the police were
OL,15,Fadvised to not reveal that
OL,16,Finformation," Imam Hussein said. "So
OL,17,Fif they were advised, we can't really
OL,18,Fblame them later on. But we suffered
OL,19,Ffor them not releasing the full
OL,20,Finformation."
