OL,6,F"I think anyone who has abused this
OL,7,Fsocial media space should come under
OL,8,Fthe full force of the law," he added.
OL,9,F"There is no need to spread false
OL,10,Finformation. You're not aware of the
OL,11,Fconsequences it could have."
OL,13,FCommittee chairwoman, Dame Karen
OL,14,FBradley, said: "It is a grim reality
OL,15,Fthat bad actors sought to exploit the
OL,16,Funspeakable tragedy that unfolded in
OL,17,FSouthport.
