OL,6,F"The criminal justice system will need
OL,7,Fto ensure its approach to
OL,8,Fcommunication is fit for the social
OL,9,Fmedia age. Lessons must be learned
OL,10,Ffrom how the whole criminal justice
OL,11,Fsystem worked together."
OL,13,FThe committee also noted that joint
OL,14,Fworking between the Government, police
OL,15,Fand criminal justice system had been
OL,16,F"essential" in bringing swift justice
OL,17,Fto those who carried out the violent
OL,18,Fdisorder.
