OL,6,FBut MPs said they agreed with policing
OL,7,Fminister Diana Johnson that it was not
OL,8,Fright for other serious crimes to see
OL,9,Fsignificant delays to justice.
OL,11,FThe report said: "The Government's
OL,12,Fbroader ambitions to reduce crime will
OL,13,Frequire better long-term alignment
OL,14,Fbetween Home Office policies on crime
OL,15,Fand policing and those of the Ministry
OL,16,Fof Justice relating to the criminal
OL,17,Fjustice system and the prison estate."
